1
00:00:01,970 --> 00:00:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I—this me—</font>

2
00:00:04,460 --> 00:00:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">hasn't given you the Key yet.</font>

3
00:00:08,270 --> 00:00:11,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for me to repay you. 
With a world that you can keep living in.</font>

4
00:00:12,620 --> 00:00:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you're precious to me.</font>

5
00:00:17,990 --> 00:00:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Setsu"?</font>

6
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That person doesn't exist IRL!</font>

7
00:00:22,910 --> 00:00:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

8
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not really sure, but...</font>

9
00:00:27,550 --> 00:00:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu's already gone,</font>

10
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but don't they still have to give the Key 
to the you of <i>this</i> universe?</font>

11
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

12
00:00:35,370 --> 00:00:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was bored, so I compiled it all.</font>

13
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything that'll happen henceforth, 
and everything you'll need to do.</font>

14
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is the Hoshibune.</font>

15
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu!</font>

16
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand?</font>

17
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 21: END POINT AND STARTING POINT</font>

18
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you wouldn't, considering how 
dated this instant learning system is.</font>

19
00:01:08,630 --> 00:01:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 1: STARTING POINT</font>

20
00:01:12,390 --> 00:01:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you get up?</font>

21
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me ask you this first.</font>

22
00:01:24,250 --> 00:01:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think humanity should 
be erased from this universe?</font>

23
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

24
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They shouldn't.</font>

25
00:01:31,790 --> 00:01:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

26
00:01:33,370 --> 00:01:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how many liars are among them.</font>

27
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri, you're...</font>

28
00:01:42,170 --> 00:01:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otome remembered you.</font>

29
00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently she felt a pain in her lip 
when she heard your name.</font>

30
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be... N-No...</font>

31
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why?!</font>

32
00:01:55,010 --> 00:01:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used the Silver Key 
to open the door again.</font>

33
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I could end your looping, Setsu.</font>

34
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Again"?</font>

35
00:02:06,110 --> 00:02:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. This time it took really long.</font>

36
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least ten times longer than last time.</font>

37
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would you do that?</font>

38
00:02:14,820 --> 00:02:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you already. To end your looping.</font>

39
00:02:20,860 --> 00:02:23,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The others made me realize something.</font>

40
00:02:23,140 --> 00:02:28,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't give me the Silver Key, 
you'll never stop looping.</font>

41
00:02:28,490 --> 00:02:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to give it to the me 
who lives in the other world,</font>

42
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like you did at the very start,</font>

43
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or cause and effect will never connect.</font>

44
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't mean—</font>

45
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to hurry.</font>

46
00:02:39,890 --> 00:02:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, I'm basically 
a ghost—my consciousness alone</font>

47
00:02:42,580 --> 00:02:44,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has been transferred into 
the body of the real me.</font>

48
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't stay for long.</font>

49
00:02:47,170 --> 00:02:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the real me regains consciousness, 
I won't be able to stay here any longer.</font>

50
00:02:52,180 --> 00:02:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you need to give me the 
Silver Key before that.</font>

51
00:02:55,610 --> 00:03:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Silver Key that opened the way here 
should be looking for a new host.</font>

52
00:03:00,270 --> 00:03:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure it's still nearby.</font>

53
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

54
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're too late.</font>

55
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to keep you waiting.</font>

56
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, the guest of honor has arrived.</font>

57
00:03:34,670 --> 00:03:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, right. This is when I first woke up.</i></font>

58
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Before I first received the Silver Key.</i></font>

59
00:03:41,610 --> 00:03:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work, Setsu.</font>

60
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has their memory come back?</font>

61
00:03:45,530 --> 00:03:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, n-no...</font>

62
00:03:48,410 --> 00:03:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what? So they've got, 
like, zero memories?</font>

63
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't that make things difficult?</font>

64
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, it's rather simple.</font>

65
00:03:55,510 --> 00:03:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just need to put them 
into cold sleep.</font>

66
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If the meeting keeps going like this...</i></font>

67
00:04:03,590 --> 00:04:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Racio will end up in cold sleep.</i></font>

68
00:04:08,010 --> 00:04:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like we have any way 
of knowing who it is for sure,</font>

69
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so let's just go ahead and... vote!</font>

70
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait!</font>

71
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no idea what's going 
on here! Vote for what?</font>

72
00:04:23,890 --> 00:04:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are Gnosia?</font>

73
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feigning ignorance even now? 
You embarrass yourself.</font>

74
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">LeVi, you heard our conversation 
just now, didn't you?</font>

75
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes. I heard everything.</i></font>

76
00:04:35,420 --> 00:04:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you give us just a little 
more time before the meeting?</font>

77
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have much time.</font>

78
00:04:44,790 --> 00:04:47,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to explain, 
hurry up and get it over with.</font>

79
00:04:48,970 --> 00:04:50,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to make some coffee.</font>

80
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then use this.</font>

81
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone gave it to me in Liu-An.</font>

82
00:04:57,730 --> 00:05:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's weird. I could've 
sworn I put it here.</font>

83
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't find it?</font>

84
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I think it's in my room.</font>

85
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead and start talking. 
I'll be right back.</font>

86
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, now.</font>

87
00:05:10,570 --> 00:05:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're we supposed to even talk about?</font>

88
00:05:13,090 --> 00:05:15,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How 'bout what we did that night?</font>

89
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually...</font>

90
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, could you tell me 
all of your names?</font>

91
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go and get the Silver Key.</font>

92
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And give it to me before 
the meeting is over.</font>

93
00:05:31,430 --> 00:05:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then your Key will be filled 
and leave your body,</font>

94
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:37,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and your looping can end.</font>

95
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all basically just met, too.</font>

96
00:05:48,030 --> 00:05:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say that Gnosia'll lie about 
anything to save their own skin.</font>

97
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let's just go with our gut 
and decide in a flash!</font>

98
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a real slowpoke, Setsu.</font>

99
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. It took a while to find.</font>

100
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is time.</i></font>

101
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please begin the meeting.</i></font>

102
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:15,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess the coffee will have to wait.</font>

103
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:28,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now Setsu just has to give me 
the Silver Key they have.</i></font>

104
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're being suspiciously sneaky.</font>

105
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

106
00:06:34,590 --> 00:06:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be keeping an eye on you until 
we get to the main control room.</font>

107
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't be sneaking away this time.</font>

108
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure, got it.</font>

109
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Crap. I wanted to get away from the others
so Setsu could give me the Silver Key...</i></font>

110
00:06:48,350 --> 00:06:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a bit drastic, 
but I have no choice.</i></font>

111
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu.</font>

112
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

113
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu, is this...</font>

114
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Wha?</font>

115
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that Silver Key...</font>

116
00:07:03,730 --> 00:07:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu, did you go into my room 
without permission?</font>

117
00:07:10,690 --> 00:07:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Come back here!</font>

118
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

119
00:07:16,350 --> 00:07:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry!</font>

120
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have a thief in our midst!
Capture them!</font>

121
00:07:25,150 --> 00:07:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously... how reckless 
are you planning to be?</font>

122
00:07:30,110 --> 00:07:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I mean... It did sorta belong 
to me in the first place...</font>

123
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:37,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're too slow!</font>

124
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:06,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is no laughing matter. 
Now they think I'm a thief.</font>

125
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

126
00:08:08,090 --> 00:08:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm pretty sure 
Racio will forgive you.</font>

127
00:08:11,790 --> 00:08:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

128
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. In fact, I'm certain of it.</font>

129
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we'll finally both be able 
to stop looping.</font>

130
00:08:27,010 --> 00:08:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be able to connect 
all of the cause and effect.</font>

131
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:32,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Finally.</font>

132
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu?</font>

133
00:08:37,730 --> 00:08:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

134
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that I'll finally be able 
to stop looping.</font>

135
00:08:44,710 --> 00:08:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what's going to happen to you, Yuri?</font>

136
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you accept this, you'll have 
to start looping again...</font>

137
00:08:54,010 --> 00:08:55,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay.</font>

138
00:08:55,950 --> 00:08:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only one who has to 
end up as its host is me.</font>

139
00:08:59,980 --> 00:09:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came from another universe, and I 
shouldn't even exist in the first place.</font>

140
00:09:04,370 --> 00:09:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just a Bug that'll disappear soon.</font>

141
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disappear?</font>

142
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:12,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

143
00:09:13,970 --> 00:09:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I asked for 
when I came over here.</font>

144
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked them to make me disappear 
once everything was over.</font>

145
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To return the universe to a Bugless state.</font>

146
00:09:24,770 --> 00:09:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When that happens, the Silver Key 
should disappear along with me.</font>

147
00:09:32,990 --> 00:09:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. That can't happen.</font>

148
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a Bug, I threw the universe 
into chaos by existing,</font>

149
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm going to return everything back 
to normal like nothing ever happened</font>

150
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and disappear.</font>

151
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't imagine living a more 
beautiful life than that.</font>

152
00:09:53,070 --> 00:09:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please...</font>

153
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see this through.</font>

154
00:09:57,950 --> 00:09:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no time left.</font>

155
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu!</font>

156
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

157
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">-Doubt not, fear not, and know.
-Yuri...</font>

158
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowledge will save all.</font>

159
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think... I'm still okay.</font>

160
00:10:37,950 --> 00:10:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri...</font>

161
00:10:46,290 --> 00:10:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yuri, Setsu.</i></font>

162
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is past time for the meeting to begin.</i></font>

163
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I repeat.</i></font>

164
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Yuri, Setsu.</i></font>

165
00:10:54,730 --> 00:10:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we still have 
something we need to do.</font>

166
00:10:55,310 --> 00:10:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It is past time for the meeting to begin.</i></font>

167
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:14,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late, you thieves.</font>

168
00:11:14,490 --> 00:11:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just finished deciding 
to send you both into cold sleep.</font>

169
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We didn't decide anything.</font>

170
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just what <i>you</i> think we should do.</font>

171
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who wouldn't?</font>

172
00:11:23,970 --> 00:11:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They had the nerve the commit 
grand larceny on this tiny ship!</font>

173
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can they be anything but Gnosia?</font>

174
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your logic is failing.</font>

175
00:11:30,210 --> 00:11:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like you just have 
a grudge, to be honest.</font>

176
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please begin the meeting.</i></font>

177
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

178
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph!</font>

179
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies.</font>

180
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the interest of ending this meeting, 
there was something we needed to do,</font>

181
00:11:43,630 --> 00:11:45,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we were a bit late.</font>

182
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ending this meeting?</font>

183
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:49,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

184
00:11:51,210 --> 00:11:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to end this meeting</font>

185
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without sacrificing anyone.</font>

186
00:11:58,290 --> 00:12:01,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph. You're just making stuff up now.</font>

187
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:04,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kukrushka?</font>

188
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

189
00:12:05,410 --> 00:12:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the universe where you didn't exist, 
Kukrushka was also never part of the crew.</font>

190
00:12:10,850 --> 00:12:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She remained a doll.</font>

191
00:12:14,420 --> 00:12:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any idea why?</font>

192
00:12:16,970 --> 00:12:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

193
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go to the main control room.</font>

194
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll settle all of this 
through conversation.</font>

195
00:12:24,730 --> 00:12:30,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've relied on you entirely too much, 
so let me handle it this time.</font>

196
00:12:32,230 --> 00:12:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Setsu...</i></font>

197
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me say this right off the bat.</font>

198
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Gnosia is SQ.</font>

199
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

200
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who, me?!</font>

201
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, though?</font>

202
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There it is.</font>

203
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuri and I already know 
without even having to discuss it.</font>

204
00:12:50,330 --> 00:12:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my...</font>

205
00:12:52,070 --> 00:12:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a closer look. It's already 
filled to the brim with knowledge.</font>

206
00:12:55,740 --> 00:12:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not the one that I got 
from your room earlier.</font>

207
00:12:59,590 --> 00:13:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This Silver Key is already full.</font>

208
00:13:02,210 --> 00:13:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know what that means?</font>

209
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So you've already 
experienced looping.</font>

210
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looping?</font>

211
00:13:11,150 --> 00:13:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I've already experienced the 
same period of time hundreds of times</font>

212
00:13:15,970 --> 00:13:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and obtained all kinds of information.</font>

213
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why I know it's you,</font>

214
00:13:20,970 --> 00:13:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Manan.</font>

215
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Manan"?</font>

216
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, Manan...</font>

217
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've looped many times, and I've spent 
more of them than I can count with her.</font>

218
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The real SQ that you failed 
to transfer your consciousness to</font>

219
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who always refers to herself 
as "cute li'l SQ."</font>

220
00:13:39,730 --> 00:13:41,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The real SQ?</font>

221
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. The one who's here 
right now is Manan.</font>

222
00:13:45,330 --> 00:13:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's SQ's mother, who transferred 
her consciousness to SQ's body.</font>

223
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The proof is... that she hasn't once 
called herself "cute li'l SQ."</font>

224
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that true?</font>

225
00:13:58,490 --> 00:14:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welp, looks like the 
cat's out of the bag.</font>

226
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:04,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've really done your homework.</font>

227
00:14:04,620 --> 00:14:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're admitting it?</font>

228
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, though, wasn't there something 
more worthwhile to spend your time on?</font>

229
00:14:12,810 --> 00:14:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup! You bet your ass I'm Manan!</font>

230
00:14:16,740 --> 00:14:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you do admit it.</font>

231
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but... so what?</font>

232
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I'm Manan, that 
doesn't make me a Gnosia.</font>

233
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It does, actually.</font>

234
00:14:29,930 --> 00:14:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I continued looping, there was one 
thing I always wondered about SQ.</font>

235
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The real SQ that resulted from Manan's 
transfer of consciousness failing,</font>

236
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the fully Manan SQ that 
resulted from it succeeding...</font>

237
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What determined which one appeared?</font>

238
00:14:48,210 --> 00:14:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to know the answer, so I 
gathered data across hundreds of loops</font>

239
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:53,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and finally figured it out.</font>

240
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Manan... only appears when 
SQ is infected by the Gnosia.</font>

241
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How amusing! So that's why 
you said she was a Gnosia.</font>

242
00:15:06,010 --> 00:15:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She fell right into your trap.</font>

243
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's just making stuff up!</font>

244
00:15:10,680 --> 00:15:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no proof behind 
anything she just said!</font>

245
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't deny that. 
If the others decide I'm lying,</font>

246
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who'll be chosen.</font>

247
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The votes will tell us everything.</font>

248
00:15:27,010 --> 00:15:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is time.</i></font>

249
00:15:28,650 --> 00:15:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We will now change over 
to the voting process.</i></font>

250
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You may not veto the result.</i></font>

251
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The voting result will be deemed 
to be the will of all present,</i></font>

252
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and you will abide by it.</i></font>

253
00:15:45,590 --> 00:15:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do you agree?</i></font>

254
00:15:51,090 --> 00:15:54,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then it is time for the verdict.</i></font>

255
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who is the Gnosia?</i></font>

256
00:16:15,020 --> 00:16:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Voting has completed. Five valid votes.</i></font>

257
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The voting rate is 100%.</i></font>

258
00:16:21,390 --> 00:16:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The votes will now be tallied.</i></font>

259
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:37,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It has been decided.</i></font>

260
00:16:38,140 --> 00:16:41,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>SQ will be put into cold sleep.</i></font>

261
00:16:42,810 --> 00:16:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, there's no need for that.</font>

262
00:16:45,350 --> 00:16:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to settle this 
without the need for cold sleep.</font>

263
00:16:48,370 --> 00:16:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously? You're still not done?</font>

264
00:16:50,810 --> 00:16:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. I said I'd end this 
without sacrificing anyone.</font>

265
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This meeting—and this story.</font>

266
00:16:56,940 --> 00:17:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">LeVi, could you open 
container 1375 in storage?</font>

267
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm terribly sorry.</i></font>

268
00:17:04,050 --> 00:17:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The ship's hold is locked 
under the captain's authority.</i></font>

269
00:17:07,770 --> 00:17:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Jonas isn't here.</font>

270
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm with the military. I have the right 
to perform a search of the cargo on board.</font>

271
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

272
00:17:16,010 --> 00:17:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You heard everything we just said, 
didn't you, LeVi?</font>

273
00:17:19,860 --> 00:17:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or should I say... Stella?</font>

274
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stella... So you're going 
to call me by that name.</i></font>

275
00:17:26,870 --> 00:17:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I'm asking you...</font>

276
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stella.</font>

277
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:37,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're telling me to enter 
this doll's body instead?</font>

278
00:17:37,370 --> 00:17:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you serious?</font>

279
00:17:38,840 --> 00:17:42,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then I'll have you 
go to another universe.</font>

280
00:17:42,150 --> 00:17:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will open the door.</font>

281
00:17:47,150 --> 00:17:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you're no stranger 
to transferring your own consciousness.</font>

282
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, but I mean... 
Let's just think about this.</font>

283
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your sense of self is 
a super-delicate thing.</font>

284
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I transfer over,</font>

285
00:17:58,650 --> 00:18:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's possible my personality 
might get ripped to shreds...</font>

286
00:18:03,030 --> 00:18:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So isn't this penalty a bit harsh?</font>

287
00:18:05,610 --> 00:18:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Penalty? Don't get the wrong idea.</font>

288
00:18:08,900 --> 00:18:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't a penalty.</font>

289
00:18:11,180 --> 00:18:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

290
00:18:12,690 --> 00:18:15,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you. I have no intention 
of sacrificing anyone.</font>

291
00:18:16,530 --> 00:18:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you'll actually agree to transfer 
into that doll and go through the door.</font>

292
00:18:21,040 --> 00:18:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they okay in the head?</font>

293
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just think about it—</font>

294
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why it's better for you 
to transfer into that doll,</font>

295
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and why you're better off 
on the other side of that door.</font>

296
00:18:32,300 --> 00:18:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll no longer have to keep 
transferring your consciousness,</font>

297
00:18:35,570 --> 00:18:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">since a doll's body doesn't deteriorate.</font>

298
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And once you're through the door, 
you'll have the Silver Key to yourself.</font>

299
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be able to use it to turn 
back time as much as you want.</font>

300
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, unlike me, you want eternal life</font>

301
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and to be young forever. 
Sounds perfect for you, right?</font>

302
00:18:55,140 --> 00:19:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So that's how you're 
gonna reel me in, huh?</font>

303
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, Manan.</font>

304
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, you might fail and have 
your personality torn to shreds,</font>

305
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but at the very least, 
no one will miss you.</font>

306
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so mean!</font>

307
00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you can be sharp-tongued 
when it counts, too, Jina.</font>

308
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, you stupid Glyze bougie!</font>

309
00:19:38,220 --> 00:19:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was the transfer successful?</font>

310
00:19:40,860 --> 00:19:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. It must have been 
for her to be moving now.</font>

311
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you go through this door, 
you'll end up in another universe.</font>

312
00:19:50,530 --> 00:19:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is goodbye.</font>

313
00:20:03,170 --> 00:20:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Manan.</font>

314
00:20:06,190 --> 00:20:10,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's meet again someday.</font>

315
00:20:11,450 --> 00:20:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hopefully under better circumstances.</font>

316
00:20:32,330 --> 00:20:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess all the causes and effects 
have finally been connected.</font>

317
00:20:35,710 --> 00:20:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

318
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We will soon be commencing warp.</i></font>

319
00:20:43,130 --> 00:20:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yuri, Setsu, please return to your rooms.</i></font>

320
00:20:47,320 --> 00:20:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we're fine right here.</font>

321
00:20:49,870 --> 00:20:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As you wish.</i></font>

322
00:20:51,810 --> 00:20:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But please at least lie down.</i></font>

323
00:20:59,870 --> 00:21:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand?</font>

324
00:21:03,710 --> 00:21:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm hungry.</font>

325
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu...</font>

326
00:21:08,730 --> 00:21:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, Yuri...</font>

327
00:21:12,230 --> 00:21:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I went through the door before, 
I was prepared...</font>

328
00:21:17,770 --> 00:21:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to never see you again.</font>

329
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I was going to keep looping forever 
in a world where you didn't exist.</font>

330
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or so I thought.</font>

331
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:29,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But then...</font>

332
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came to see me again 
and you saved me.</font>

333
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You helped end my looping.</font>

334
00:21:42,630 --> 00:21:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you worked hard, too, Setsu.</font>

335
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't have been able 
to pull that last part off by myself.</font>

336
00:21:50,610 --> 00:21:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. We both worked hard.</font>

337
00:21:55,790 --> 00:22:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Through all the world lines, we crossed 
universes and ended up here.</font>

338
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally figured it out.</font>

339
00:22:06,890 --> 00:22:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are an irregularity.</font>

340
00:22:10,130 --> 00:22:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a one-of-a-kind existence 
that shows up in a universe</font>

341
00:22:13,890 --> 00:22:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that was warped by the Silver Key.</font>

342
00:22:17,140 --> 00:22:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Bug.</font>

343
00:22:19,170 --> 00:22:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's not it.</font>

344
00:22:21,100 --> 00:22:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not a Bug.</font>

345
00:22:23,540 --> 00:22:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're...</font>

346
00:22:25,950 --> 00:22:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my...</font>

347
00:22:28,410 --> 00:22:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Beginning warp countdown.</i></font>

348
00:22:32,210 --> 00:22:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Ten, nine, eight, seven, six, five,</i></font>

349
00:22:35,510 --> 00:22:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Setsu...</font>

350
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:42,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}four, three, two, one...</i></font>

351
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Yuri.</font>

352
00:22:58,210 --> 00:23:01,500
